"zh-CN">试着让一切慢慢来</span></p><p begin="5.180" end="6.985" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="5.180" end="5.349">Ya,</span> <span begin="5.349" end="5.460">we</span> <span begin="5.460" end="5.688">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="5.731" end="6.170">tal</span><span begin="6.170" end="6.219">k</span> <span begin="6.219" end="6.308">a</span><span begin="6.331" end="6.805">bout</span> <span begin="6.805" end="6.985">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们无需多言</span></p><p begin="7.479" end="9.470" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="7.479" end="7.744">Use</span> <span begin="7.744" end="7.997">your</span> <span begin="8.045" end="8.510">bo</span><span begin="8.510" end="8.650">dy</span> <span begin="8.650" end="9.090">lan</span><span begin="9.090" end="9.318">gua</span><span begin="9.318" end="9.470">ge</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只用你的肢体语言</span></p><p begin="9.800" end="11.731" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="9.800" end="10.022">Cause</span> <span begin="10.022" end="10.292">your</span> <span begin="10.344" end="10.678">move</span><span begin="10.678" end="10.947">ment</span> <span begin="10.947" end="11.212">says</span> <span begin="11.212" end="11.369">it</span> <span begin="11.369" end="11.731">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为你的举动说明了一切</span></p><p begin="12.403" end="14.090" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.403" end="12.566">And</span> <span begin="12.566" end="12.670">I</span> <span begin="12.670" end="13.043">tried</span> <span begin="13.043" end="13.261">to</span> <span begin="13.261" end="13.510">shake</span> <span begin="13.510" end="13.679">it</span> <span begin="13.679" end="14.090">off</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我尝试过在脑海里甩掉你的影子</span></p><p begin="14.440" end="16.274" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.440" end="14.540">But</span> <span begin="14.540" end="14.712">there&apos;s</span> <span begin="14.712" end="14.974">no</span> <span begin="14.974" end="15.433">way</span> <span begin="15.433" end="15.527">a</span><span begin="15.527" end="15.997">round</span> <span begin="15.997" end="16.274">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但都无济于事</span></p><p begin="16.718" end="18.520" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.718" end="16.904">I</span> <span begin="16.904" end="17.083">know</span> <span begin="17.083" end="17.282">it</span> <span begin="17.282" end="17.718">sounds</span> <span begin="17.718" end="17.877">dra</span><span begin="17.877" end="18.277">mat</span><span begin="18.277" end="18.520">ic</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">听上去我是那样荒诞不经</span></p><p begin="18.732" end="20.550" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="18.732" end="18.913">But</span> <span begin="18.980" end="19.364">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="19.364" end="19.611">the</span> <span begin="19.611" end="20.112">one</span> <span begin="20.162" end="20.550">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你是我心中唯一存在</span></p><p begin="20.767" end="23.276" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.767" end="21.312">On</span><span begin="21.312" end="21.660">ly</span> <span begin="21.873" end="22.107">thing</span> <span begin="22.212" end="22.435">on</span> <span begin="22.488" end="22.699">my</span> <span begin="22.788" end="23.276">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是我脑海里仅有的爱</span></p><p begin="23.624" end="26.685" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="23.624" end="23.870">Guess</span> <span begin="23.870" end="24.133">I</span> <span begin="24.206" end="24.488">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="24.488" end="24.821">run</span> <span begin="24.821" end="25.040">a</span><span begin="25.105" end="25.673">way</span> <span begin="25.954" end="26.208">this</span> <span begin="26.273" end="26.685">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这次我已无法逃脱</span></p><p begin="27.967" end="29.701" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="27.967" end="28.221">When</span> <span begin="28.221" end="28.494">I</span> <span begin="28.494" end="28.730">say</span> <span begin="28.801" end="29.701">baby</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝</span></p><p begin="29.982" end="32.504" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.982" end="30.550">On</span><span begin="30.550" end="30.861">ly</span> <span begin="31.118" end="31.433">you</span> <span begin="31.433" end="31.603">make</span> <span begin="31.691" end="32.027">it</span> <span begin="32.027" end="32.504">right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只有你是我一生最值得托付的人</span></p><p begin="32.733" end="35.920" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.733" end="32.866">So</span> <span begin="32.866" end="33.181">if</span> <span begin="33.181" end="33.450">we</span> <span begin="33.450" end="33.705">live</span> <span begin="33.705" end="33.852">and</span> <span begin="33.852" end="34.218">die</span> <span begin="34.218" end="34.390">we</span> <span begin="34.390" end="34.558">should</span> <span begin="34.558" end="34.844">do</span> <span begin="34.844" end="34.995">it</span> <span begin="34.995" end="35.123">to</span><span begin="35.123" end="35.681">geth</span><span begin="35.681" end="35.920">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果生死相随 我们就共进退</span></p><p begin="38.035" end="38.916" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.035" end="38.203">Come</span> <span begin="38.203" end="38.362">on,</span> <span begin="38.362" end="38.600">let&apos;s</span> <span begin="38.600" end="38.916">fly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一起飞吧</span></p><p begin="38.942" end="40.319" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.942" end="39.078">Like</span> <span begin="39.078" end="39.177">an</span> <span begin="39.221" end="39.687">air</span><span begin="39.804" end="40.319">plane</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像乘一艘爱的飞船</span></p><p begin="40.361" end="42.517" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.361" end="40.635">Maybe</span> <span begin="40.635" end="40.832">we&apos;ll</span> <span begin="40.888" end="41.171">go</span> <span begin="41.171" end="41.351">set</span><span begin="41.351" end="41.479">tle</span> <span begin="41.515" end="41.809">down</span> <span begin="41.809" end="42.006">one</span> <span begin="42.103" end="42.517">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也许有天我们能心意坚定</span></p><p begin="42.956" end="44.838" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.956" end="43.122">Mess</span> <span begin="43.122" end="43.185">a</span><span begin="43.185" end="43.498">round</span> <span begin="43.498" end="43.668">till</span> <span begin="43.668" end="43.802">you</span> <span begin="43.827" end="44.056">take</span> <span begin="44.119" end="44.326">my</span> <span begin="44.398" end="44.838">name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到你也能将我的名字刻在心底</span></p><p begin="45.243" end="46.991" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="45.243" end="45.838">Maybe</span> <span begin="46.087" end="46.412">one</span> <span begin="46.412" end="46.991">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="47.246" end="49.588" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.246" end="47.369">Is</span> <span begin="47.369" end="47.573">it</span> <span begin="47.573" end="47.813">my</span> <span begin="47.813" end="48.085">heart</span> <span begin="48.085" end="48.299">soar</span><span begin="48.299" end="48.428">ing</span> <span begin="48.428" end="48.704">in</span> <span begin="48.704" end="48.900">the</span> <span begin="48.900" end="49.588">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的心还悬浮天际吗</span></p><p begin="49.612" end="51.755" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.612" end="49.732">Noth</span><span begin="49.732" end="49.892">ing</span> <span begin="49.892" end="50.148">I</span> <span begin="50.172" end="50.445">do</span> <span begin="50.445" end="50.605">get</span> <span begin="50.605" end="50.741">you</span> <span begin="50.741" end="50.906">off</span> <span begin="51.032" end="51.245">my</span> <span begin="51.327" end="51.755">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论我做什么 你总在我脑海里挥之不去</span></p><p begin="52.174" end="54.109" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.174" end="52.410">Think</span> <span begin="52.486" end="52.678">too</span> <span begin="52.678" end="52.938">hard</span> <span begin="52.938" end="53.021">I</span> <span begin="53.052" end="53.285">just</span> <span begin="53.338" end="53.535">might</span> <span begin="53.616" end="54.109">cry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">再想下去我可能会忍不住落泪</span></p><p begin="54.502" end="56.235" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.502" end="55.024">Maybe</span> <span begin="55.311" end="55.645">one</span> <span begin="55.645" end="56.235">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="59.984" end="1:01.708" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.984" end="1:00.523">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:00.523" end="1:00.807">one</span> <span begin="1:00.807" end="1:01.708">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="1:03.709" end="1:05.138" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.709" end="1:04.327">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:04.579" end="1:04.878">one</span> <span begin="1:04.878" end="1:05.138">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="1:05.167" end="1:06.311" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.167" end="1:05.447">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:05.447" end="1:05.727">one</span> <span begin="1:05.727" end="1:06.311">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="1:09.220" end="1:11.012" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.220" end="1:09.740">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:09.765" end="1:10.080">one</span> <span begin="1:10.080" end="1:11.012">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="1:12.958" end="1:14.605" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.958" end="1:13.520">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:13.759" end="1:14.102">one</span> <span begin="1:14.102" end="1:14.605">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="1:14.663" end="1:16.427" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.663" end="1:14.778">All</span> <span begin="1:14.778" end="1:14.873">it</span> <span begin="1:14.908" end="1:15.117">took</span> <span begin="1:15.243" end="1:15.474">was</span> <span begin="1:15.474" end="1:15.645">a</span> <span begin="1:15.645" end="1:15.801">s</span><span begin="1:15.801" end="1:16.300">par</span><span begin="1:16.300" end="1:16.427">k</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">爱像一簇火花</span></p><p begin="1:16.989" end="1:18.700" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.989" end="1:17.097">And</span> <span begin="1:17.097" end="1:17.194">now</span> <span begin="1:17.247" end="1:17.407">look</span> <span begin="1:17.547" end="1:17.877">where</span> <span begin="1:17.877" end="1:18.080">we</span> <span begin="1:18.151" end="1:18.700">are</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想象我现在身在何方</span></p><p begin="1:19.017" end="1:21.025" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:19.017" end="1:19.118">Go</span><span begin="1:19.118" end="1:19.325">ing</span> <span begin="1:19.325" end="1:19.527">to</span> <span begin="1:19.527" end="1:19.996">high</span><span begin="1:19.996" end="1:20.118">er</span> <span begin="1:20.160" end="1:21.025">places</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能飞往更高的地方</span></p><p begin="1:21.335" end="1:23.158" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.335" end="1:21.500">I</span> <span begin="1:21.592" end="1:21.806">can</span> <span begin="1:21.904" end="1:22.303">al</span><span begin="1:22.303" end="1:22.475">most</span> <span begin="1:22.475" end="1:22.858">taste</span> <span begin="1:22.911" end="1:23.158">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能几乎触碰到你</span></p><p begin="1:23.653" end="1:25.648" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.653" end="1:23.918">If</span> <span begin="1:23.918" end="1:24.131">we</span> <span begin="1:24.206" end="1:24.510">bump</span> <span begin="1:24.510" end="1:24.957">into</span> <span begin="1:24.957" end="1:25.648">stars</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果我们此时撞上星辰</span></p><p begin="1:26.220" end="1:27.832" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:26.220" end="1:26.353">Let</span> <span begin="1:26.353" end="1:26.511">it</span> <span begin="1:26.511" end="1:26.819">burn</span> <span begin="1:26.819" end="1:27.017">like</span> <span begin="1:27.085" end="1:27.275">my</span> <span begin="1:27.275" end="1:27.832">heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就让它燃烧像我心般深沉</span></p><p begin="1:28.079" end="1:30.184" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:28.079" end="1:28.252">It&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:28.252" end="1:28.411">like</span> <span begin="1:28.411" end="1:28.546">you</span> <span begin="1:28.546" end="1:28.688">know</span> <span begin="1:28.688" end="1:28.810">me</span> <span begin="1:28.810" end="1:28.986">in</span><span begin="1:28.986" end="1:29.414">side</span> <span begin="1:29.414" end="1:29.715">and</span> <span begin="1:29.715" end="1:30.184">out</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就像你了解我每处灵魂</span></p><p begin="1:30.453" end="1:32.798" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:30.453" end="1:30.578">And</span> <span begin="1:30.578" end="1:30.848">baby</span> <span begin="1:30.848" end="1:31.005">I</span> <span begin="1:31.005" end="1:31.130">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:31.130" end="1:31.418">know</span> <span begin="1:31.459" end="1:32.475">how</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝 此刻我不知如何是好</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:32.101" end="1:32.798"><span begin="1:32.101" end="1:32.798">(How)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如何是好</span></span></p><p begin="1:32.586" end="1:34.410" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.586" end="1:32.750">But</span> <span begin="1:32.812" end="1:33.212">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="1:33.212" end="1:33.501">the</span> <span begin="1:33.501" end="1:34.038">one</span> <span begin="1:34.038" end="1:34.410">thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你是我心中唯一存在</span></p><p begin="1:34.619" end="1:37.128" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.619" end="1:35.167">On</span><span begin="1:35.167" end="1:35.621">ly</span> <span begin="1:35.715" end="1:36.004">thing</span> <span begin="1:36.054" end="1:36.300">on</span> <span begin="1:36.345" end="1:36.533">my</span> <span begin="1:36.652" end="1:37.128">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是我脑海里仅存的爱</span></p><p begin="1:37.481" end="1:40.589" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:37.481" end="1:37.774">Guess</span> <span begin="1:37.774" end="1:37.973">I</span> <span begin="1:38.051" end="1:38.352">can&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:38.352" end="1:38.650">run</span> <span begin="1:38.650" end="1:38.922">a</span><span begin="1:38.989" end="1:39.543">way</span> <span begin="1:39.826" end="1:40.040">this</span> <span begin="1:40.088" end="1:40.589">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这次我已无法逃脱</span></p><p begin="1:41.830" end="1:43.569" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.830" end="1:42.050">When</span> <span begin="1:42.050" end="1:42.355">I</span> <span begin="1:42.355" end="1:42.580">say</span> <span begin="1:42.667" end="1:43.569">baby</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">宝贝</span></p><p begin="1:43.827" end="1:46.360" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:43.827" end="1:44.403">On</span><span begin="1:44.403" end="1:44.719">ly</span> <span begin="1:44.959" end="1:45.262">you</span> <span begin="1:45.262" end="1:45.469">make</span> <span begin="1:45.536" end="1:45.841">it</span> <span begin="1:45.841" end="1:46.360">right</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只有你是我一生最值得托付的人</span></p><p begin="1:46.555" end="1:49.752" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:46.555" end="1:46.726">So</span> <span begin="1:46.726" end="1:46.967">if</span> <span begin="1:47.005" end="1:47.269">we</span> <span begin="1:47.269" end="1:47.526">live</span> <span begin="1:47.526" end="1:47.694">and</span> <span begin="1:47.694" end="1:48.125">die</span> <span begin="1:48.125" end="1:48.243">we</span> <span begin="1:48.243" end="1:48.406">should</span> <span begin="1:48.406" end="1:48.673">do</span> <span begin="1:48.673" end="1:48.833">it</span> <span begin="1:48.833" end="1:48.988">to</span><span begin="1:48.988" end="1:49.534">geth</span><span begin="1:49.534" end="1:49.752">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果生死相随 我们就共进退</span></p><p begin="1:51.851" end="1:52.741" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.851" end="1:52.041">Come</span> <span begin="1:52.041" end="1:52.195">on</span> <span begin="1:52.195" end="1:52.471">let&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:52.471" end="1:52.741">fly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一起飞吧</span></p><p begin="1:52.767" end="1:54.190" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.767" end="1:52.910">Like</span> <span begin="1:52.910" end="1:53.066">an</span> <span begin="1:53.066" end="1:53.530">air</span><span begin="1:53.649" end="1:54.190">plane</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像乘一艘爱的飞船</span></p><p begin="1:54.221" end="1:56.453" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.221" end="1:54.501">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:54.501" end="1:54.674">we&apos;ll</span> <span begin="1:54.751" end="1:55.034">go</span> <span begin="1:55.034" end="1:55.192">set</span><span begin="1:55.192" end="1:55.314">tle</span> <span begin="1:55.353" end="1:55.609">down</span> <span begin="1:55.609" end="1:55.844">one</span> <span begin="1:55.926" end="1:56.453">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也许有天我们能心意坚定</span></p><p begin="1:56.833" end="1:58.672" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.833" end="1:56.960">Mess</span> <span begin="1:56.960" end="1:57.083">a</span><span begin="1:57.083" end="1:57.361">round</span> <span begin="1:57.361" end="1:57.505">till</span> <span begin="1:57.505" end="1:57.639">you</span> <span begin="1:57.660" end="1:57.897">take</span> <span begin="1:57.950" end="1:58.184">my</span> <span begin="1:58.244" end="1:58.672">name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到你也能将我的名字刻在心底</span></p><p begin="1:59.119" end="2:00.840" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.119" end="1:59.706">Maybe</span> <span begin="1:59.983" end="2:00.270">one</span> <span begin="2:00.270" end="2:00.840">day</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在有朝一日</span></p><p begin="2:01.100" end="2:03.418" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:01.100" end="2:01.202">Is</span> <span begin="2:01.202" end="2:01.428">it</span> <span begin="2:01.428" end="2:01.648">my</span> <span begin="2:01.648" end="2:01.944">heart</span> <span begin="2:01.944" end="2:02.123">soar</span><span begin="2:02.123" end="2:02.286">ing</span> <span begin="2:02.286" end="2:02.515">in</span> <span begin="2:02.515" end="2:02.725">the</span> <span begin="2:02.725" end="2:03.418">sky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的心还悬浮天际吗</span></p><p begin="2:03.452" end="2:05.685" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.452" end="2:03.601">Noth</span><span begin="2:03.601" end="2:03.747">ing</span> <span begin="2:03.747" end="2:04.009">I</span> <span begin="2:04.032" end="2:04.317">do</span> <span begin="2:04.317" end="2:04.450">ge